    "title": "Mateso ya Kikristo",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "mateso ya kikristo",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Hatupaswi kushangaa tunapopitia mateso (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12\">1 Petro 4:12</a>). Wakristo wanaoishi kwa kumtii Mungu wanapaswa kutarajia utamaduni kujibu kwa uhasama. Tunapaswa kutarajia kejeli, matibabu mabaya, mashtaka ya uongo, na hata vurugu.</p><p>Mungu ana kusudi kwa ajili yetu katika mateso. Inatuunganisha zaidi na Kristo, ambaye aliteseka kabla ya Mungu kumtukuza (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1 Petro 4:13</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">Warumi 8:17</a>). Kwa kuteseka na Kristo, tunaweza kuwa na uhakika wa kushiriki katika utukufu ambao tayari amepata.</p><p>Barua ya 1 Petro inasisitiza mateso ya Kikristo, hasa mateso yasiyo ya haki kutoka kwa wale wanaopinga imani ya Kikristo. Mada hizi za mateso zinaelezwa kwa uwazi zaidi katika <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">4:12–19</a>.</p><p>Tunahitaji kujitolea kufanya yaliyo sahihi tunapopitia mateso (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1 Petro 4:19</a>). Magumu mara nyingi yanaweza kuwa visingizio vya kutenda dhambi. Hata hivyo, wakati wa nyakati ngumu, tunapaswa kuishi kama mifano mizuri kwa kuonyesha upendo kwa wengine. Jibu letu la upendo kwa maadui wakati wa dhiki linaweza kuwa nafasi yenye nguvu ya kushiriki imani yetu ya Kikristo. Tunapoonyesha upendo na wema kwa wale wanaotuumiza, wengine wanaweza kuvutiwa na imani yetu.</p><p>Tunapaswa kukumbuka wakati wa dhiki zetu kwamba ni &quot;mapenzi ya Mungu&quot; na yeye ni &quot;Mwaminifu&quot; (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:19\">1 Petro 4:19</a>). Yeye hudhibiti hali zote za maisha. Kwa hivyo, hatuhitaji kuogopa dhiki yoyote kana kwamba inaweza kuwa nje ya usimamizi au mapenzi ya Mungu.</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:10\">Isaya 48:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:13-Isa53:12\">52:13–53:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:7-Isa63:9\">63:7–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:35-Mark10:40\">Marko 10:35–40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:41\">Matendo 5:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:16\">9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:23\">Warumi 8:17–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:5-2Cor1:7\">2 Wakorintho 1:5–7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10\">4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:10\">12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:29\">Wafilipi 1:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">Wakolosai 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:14\">1 Wathesalonike 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:5\">2 Wathesalonike 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:12\">2 Timotheo 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:9-Heb2:10\">Waebrania 2:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8\">5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:12\">13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11-Jas5:13\">Yakobo 5:11–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:19\">1 Petro 4:12–19</a></p>",
